<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,viewport-fit=cover">
<title>USYD Bible · 悉尼大学新生终极手册</title>
<meta name="description" content="面向悉尼大学语言班与正式学位国际新生的中文知识库：从 Offer、CET/DEC、签证、enrolment、选课到学生证、Apple Wallet、校园生活和求职。">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">
<style>
:root{--bg:#f4f6f8;--surface:#fff;--surface2:#f0f3f6;--text:#16181c;--muted:#69717d;--line:#dfe3e8;--accent:#9d1726;--accent2:#c18b21;--ok:#16805c;--warn:#b86e10;--danger:#b42318;--shadow:0 18px 50px rgba(34,40,52,.09);--nav:260px;--top:74px}
html[data-theme="dark"]{--bg:#101216;--surface:#181b21;--surface2:#22262e;--text:#f4f5f7;--muted:#aeb5c0;--line:#323741;--accent:#f26377;--accent2:#e3b657;--ok:#53c99c;--warn:#f4b45e;--danger:#ff7b72;--shadow:0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.28)}
*{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI","PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;line-height:1.55}button,input{font:inherit}button{color:inherit}.app{min-height:100vh}.topbar{position:fixed;z-index:50;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:var(--top);background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--surface) 90%,transparent);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 24px;gap:22px}.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;min-width:230px;cursor:pointer}.brandmark{width:42px;height:42px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--accent),#d94058);border-radius:13px;color:#fff;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800;box-shadow:0 8px 24px color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 25%,transparent)}.brandtext{display:flex;flex-direction:column}.brand strong{font-size:15px;letter-spacing:.02em}.brand small{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}.searchbar{position:relative;flex:1;max-width:780px}.searchbar svg{position:absolute;left:14px;top:13px;color:var(--muted)}.searchbar input{width:100%;height:44px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface2);border-radius:13px;padding:0 82px 0 42px;color:var(--text);outline:0}.searchbar input:focus{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 12%,transparent)}.kbd{position:absolute;right:11px;top:10px;color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;border:1px solid var(--line);padding:3px 7px;border-radius:6px}.topactions{margin-left:auto;display:flex;gap:8px}.iconbtn{width:42px;height:42px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;display:grid;place-items:center}.iconbtn:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}.sidebar{position:fixed;z-index:30;left:0;top:var(--top);bottom:0;width:var(--nav);background:var(--surface);border-right:1px solid var(--line);padding:22px 14px 40px;overflow:auto}.sidegroup{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;padding:8px 12px}.navitem{width:100%;border:0;background:transparent;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:11px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;margin:2px 0}.navitem:hover{background:var(--surface2)}.navitem.active{background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 10%,var(--surface));color:var(--accent);font-weight:700}.navicon{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;background:var(--surface2);display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px}.navcount{margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}.main{margin-left:var(--nav);padding:calc(var(--top) + 32px) clamp(22px,4vw,62px) 80px;max-width:1700px}.view{display:none}.view.active{display:block}.hero{position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:linear-gradient(135deg,color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 10%,var(--surface)),var(--surface) 58%,color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent2) 12%,var(--surface)));border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:28px;padding:clamp(34px,6vw,76px);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}.hero:after{content:"";position:absolute;width:330px;height:330px;border-radius:50%;right:-110px;top:-100px;background:radial-gradient(circle,color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent2) 28%,transparent),transparent 68%)}.eyebrow{color:var(--accent);font-weight:800;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.11em;text-transform:uppercase}.hero h1{position:relative;font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,74px);line-height:1.03;letter-spacing:-.045em;margin:17px 0;max-width:900px}.hero p{position:relative;font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,20px);color:var(--muted);max-width:820px}.actions{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:28px}.btn{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);border-radius:12px;padding:11px 16px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700}.btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}.btn.primary{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);color:#fff}.trustline{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:10px;margin-top:26px}.trustline span{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:12px;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px}.trustline b{color:var(--text);font-size:13px}.statrow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;margin:22px 0}.stat{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:21px}.stat b{font-size:29px;display:block}.stat span{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px}.sectionhead{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:end;margin:38px 0 17px}.sectionhead h2{font-size:25px;margin:0}.sectionhead p{color:var(--muted);margin:4px 0 0}.categorygrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px}.catcard,.topic{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:22px;cursor:pointer;transition:.18s}.catcard:hover,.topic:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);border-color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 40%,var(--line));box-shadow:var(--shadow)}.caticon{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:13px;background:var(--surface2);display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:19px}.catcard h3{margin:15px 0 5px}.catcard p,.topic p{margin:0;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}.catmeta{display:block;color:var(--accent);font-size:11px;margin-top:15px;font-weight:800}.facts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:11px}.fact{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:15px;padding:17px;cursor:pointer}.fact b{display:block;font-size:14px}.fact span{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px}.pagehead{margin-bottom:25px}.pagehead h1{font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px);margin:0;letter-spacing:-.04em}.pagehead p{color:var(--muted)}.filterbar{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:20px}.chip{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);border-radius:999px;padding:8px 13px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px}.chip.active{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);color:#fff}.topicgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:13px}.topic{position:relative;min-height:178px;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.topic.official-detail{border-top:4px solid var(--accent)}.topic .top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}.type{font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.06em}.fav{border:0;background:transparent;color:#aeb4bd;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px}.fav.on{color:var(--accent2)}.topic h3{font-size:17px;margin:14px 0 7px}.topicfoot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:auto;padding-top:15px;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)}.verified-badge{color:var(--ok);font-weight:800}.checkgroup{margin:30px 0}.checkgroup h2{font-size:20px}.checklist{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden}.checkrow{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:13px;padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}.checkrow:last-child{border-bottom:0}.checkrow input{appearance:none;width:22px;height:22px;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:7px;margin-top:1px;cursor:pointer;display:grid;place-items:center}.checkrow input:checked{background:var(--ok);border-color:var(--ok)}.checkrow input:checked:after{content:"✓";color:#fff;font-size:14px}.checkrow label{cursor:pointer;flex:1}.checkrow.done label{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--muted)}.progress{height:8px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden}.progress span{display:block;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));width:0}.sourcegrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px}.sourcecard{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);border-radius:14px;padding:15px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text)}.sourcecard:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}.sourcecard b{display:block}.sourcecard span{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}.emergencygrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:14px}.emcard{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:22px;background:var(--surface)}.emcard.danger{border-color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--danger) 45%,var(--line));background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--danger) 6%,var(--surface))}.emcard h3{margin-top:0}.bigphone{font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:var(--danger)}.drawerback{position:fixed;z-index:60;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.36);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:.2s}.drawerback.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}.drawer{position:fixed;z-index:61;right:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:min(620px,100%);background:var(--surface);transform:translateX(102%);transition:.25s ease;box-shadow:-20px 0 60px rgba(0,0,0,.2);padding:24px clamp(20px,4vw,42px) 50px;overflow:auto}.drawer.open{transform:none}.drawerclose{position:sticky;top:0;float:right}.drawer h1{font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,48px);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin:45px 0 15px}.drawer .summary{font-size:17px;color:var(--muted)}.callout{border-left:3px solid var(--accent2);padding:12px 15px;background:var(--surface2);margin:22px 0;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0}.steps{padding-left:22px}.steps li{margin:10px 0}.sourcebox{margin-top:28px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:20px}.sourcebox a{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none}.tagrow{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}.tag{font-size:11px;border:1px solid var(--line);padding:4px 8px;border-radius:999px;color:var(--muted)}.mobilebar{display:none}.searchpanel{display:none}.disclaimer{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 16px;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:30px}.only-print{display:none}
@media(max-width:1050px){:root{--nav:220px}.categorygrid,.topicgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.statrow{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.trustline{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:760px){:root{--top:64px}.topbar{padding:0 12px}.brand{min-width:0}.brandtext{display:none}.topbar .searchbar{display:none}.sidebar{display:none}.main{margin:0;padding:calc(var(--top) + 18px) 14px 94px}.hero{padding:28px 21px;border-radius:21px}.hero h1{font-size:40px}.hero p{font-size:15px}.trustline{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.categorygrid,.topicgrid,.facts,.sourcegrid,.emergencygrid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.mobilebar{position:fixed;z-index:49;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);left:9px;right:9px;bottom:9px;padding:7px;background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--surface) 94%,transparent);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(20px)}.mobilebar button{border:0;background:transparent;padding:7px 3px;color:var(--muted);font-size:9px;border-radius:10px}.mobilebar button b{display:block;font-size:17px}.mobilebar button.active{color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface2)}.topbar .themebtn{display:none}}
@media print{.topbar,.sidebar,.mobilebar,.actions,.filterbar,.fav,.drawerback,.drawer{display:none!important}.main{margin:0;padding:20px}.view{display:block!important}.view:not(#checklistView){display:none!important}.checkrow input{border:1px solid #000}.only-print{display:block}}

/* 2026 official-first redesign */
:root{--bg:#f7f6f3;--surface:#fff;--surface2:#f2f0ec;--text:#161616;--muted:#5f6368;--line:#d9d6d0;--accent:#b20d2f;--accent-dark:#7f0821;--accent2:#d4a33d;--ok:#137a57;--shadow:0 14px 40px rgba(27,20,18,.08);--nav:248px;--top:72px}
html[data-theme="dark"]{--bg:#111214;--surface:#181a1e;--surface2:#22252b;--text:#f5f3ef;--muted:#adb2ba;--line:#32363d;--accent:#ff667f;--accent-dark:#ff8b9e;--accent2:#e6b856;--shadow:0 18px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.28)}
body{font-family:Arial,"Helvetica Neue","PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;letter-spacing:.002em}.app:before{content:"";position:fixed;z-index:40;left:0;right:0;top:0;height:6px;background:var(--accent)}
.topbar{top:6px;height:var(--top);padding:0 26px;background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--surface) 96%,transparent);backdrop-filter:blur(18px)}.brandmark{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:none;font-family:Georgia,serif}.brand strong{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;font-size:17px}.brand small{letter-spacing:0;text-transform:none}.searchbar{max-width:680px}.searchbar input{height:46px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--surface);padding-left:45px;box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px transparent}.searchbar input:hover{background:var(--surface2)}.searchbar input:focus{background:var(--surface);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 14%,transparent)}.kbd{border-radius:3px}.iconbtn{border-radius:4px}.sidebar{top:calc(var(--top) + 6px);padding:24px 14px;background:var(--surface)}.sidegroup{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em}.navitem{border-radius:4px;padding:9px 10px}.navitem.active{box-shadow:inset 3px 0 0 var(--accent)}.navicon{border:0;background:transparent;width:22px;height:22px}.main{padding-top:calc(var(--top) + 42px);max-width:1480px}.hero{border-radius:0;border:0;border-top:7px solid var(--accent);padding:clamp(30px,5vw,64px);box-shadow:var(--shadow);background:linear-gradient(110deg,var(--surface) 0 74%,color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent2) 13%,var(--surface)) 74%)}.hero:after{display:none}.eyebrow{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.11em;text-transform:uppercase}.hero h1{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman","Songti SC",serif;font-size:clamp(42px,5.8vw,74px);line-height:1.03;letter-spacing:-.04em;max-width:820px;margin:14px 0 18px}.hero p{font-size:18px;max-width:780px}.hero-search{margin-top:30px;max-width:760px;position:relative}.hero-search input{width:100%;height:58px;border:2px solid var(--text);border-radius:0;background:var(--surface);padding:0 58px 0 48px;font-size:17px;color:var(--text);outline:0}.hero-search svg{position:absolute;left:17px;top:19px;pointer-events:none}.hero-search button{position:absolute;right:5px;top:5px;height:48px;border:0;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;padding:0 18px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer}.popular{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:13px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}.popular button{border:0;background:transparent;color:var(--accent);padding:0;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px}.actions{margin-top:25px}.btn{border-radius:3px;padding:11px 17px}.trustline{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:3px}.trustline span{border:0}.statrow{gap:1px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line)}.stat{border:0;border-radius:0;padding:25px}.stat b{font-family:Georgia,serif;color:var(--accent)}.categorygrid{gap:1px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line)}.catcard{border:0;border-radius:0;padding:25px;min-height:190px}.catcard:hover,.topic:hover{transform:none;box-shadow:none;background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 3%,var(--surface));border-color:var(--line)}.caticon{border-radius:3px;width:36px;height:36px;background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 8%,var(--surface));color:var(--accent)}.facts{gap:1px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line)}.fact{border:0;border-radius:0;padding:19px}.sectionhead{border-bottom:2px solid var(--text);padding-bottom:12px}.sectionhead h2,.pagehead h1{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman","Songti SC",serif}.pagehead{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding-bottom:20px}.pagehead h1{font-size:clamp(38px,5vw,60px)}.filterbar{position:sticky;top:calc(var(--top) + 14px);z-index:12;background:var(--bg);padding:8px 0}.chip{border-radius:3px}.topicgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line)}.topic{border:0;border-radius:0;min-height:188px;padding:24px}.topic.official-detail{border-top:5px solid var(--accent)}.topic h3{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman","Songti SC",serif;font-size:20px;line-height:1.25}.verified-badge{color:var(--accent)}.checklist{border-radius:0}.sourcegrid{gap:1px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line)}.sourcecard{border:0;border-radius:0;padding:20px}.drawer{width:min(720px,100%);padding:25px clamp(22px,5vw,56px) 70px}.drawer h1{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman","Songti SC",serif;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,55px)}.drawer h2{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman","Songti SC",serif;font-size:21px;margin-top:29px}.article-provenance{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);margin:25px 0}.article-provenance div{padding:13px;border-right:1px solid var(--line)}.article-provenance div:last-child{border:0}.article-provenance b,.article-provenance span{display:block}.article-provenance b{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--muted)}.article-provenance span{font-size:12px;margin-top:4px}.official-path{border-left:5px solid var(--accent);background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--accent) 6%,var(--surface));padding:15px 17px;margin:22px 0;font-size:14px}.article-section{border-top:1px solid var(--line);margin-top:27px;padding-top:4px}.article-section ol,.article-section ul{padding-left:23px}.article-section li{margin:11px 0;line-height:1.65}.warning-list{border-left:4px solid var(--warn);padding-left:17px}.source-link{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border:1px solid var(--line);padding:13px 15px;margin:8px 0;color:var(--text)!important}.source-link:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}.searchpanel{display:block;position:fixed;z-index:80;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.42);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:.15s}.searchpanel.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}.searchbox{position:absolute;top:10vh;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:min(760px,calc(100% - 24px));max-height:78vh;background:var(--surface);border-top:6px solid var(--accent);box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.3);display:flex;flex-direction:column}.searchinputwrap{padding:18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;gap:10px}.searchinputwrap input{flex:1;height:50px;border:1px solid var(--line);padding:0 16px;font-size:17px;background:var(--surface);color:var(--text);outline:0}.searchinputwrap input:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}.searchclose{border:0;background:var(--surface2);width:50px;cursor:pointer}.searchresults{overflow:auto;padding:8px}.searchresult{display:block;width:100%;text-align:left;border:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);padding:15px;cursor:pointer}.searchresult:hover,.searchresult.active{background:var(--surface2)}.searchresult b{display:block}.searchresult span{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}.suggestions{position:absolute;top:62px;left:0;right:0;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:var(--shadow);z-index:20;display:none}.suggestions.open{display:block}.suggestion{width:100%;border:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);padding:13px 15px;text-align:left;cursor:pointer}.suggestion:hover{background:var(--surface2)}.suggestion b{display:block}.suggestion span{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}
@media(max-width:1050px){.topicgrid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.categorygrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:760px){.app:before{height:5px}.topbar{top:5px;padding:0 13px}.main{padding-top:calc(var(--top) + 23px)}.hero{border-top-width:5px;padding:27px 21px}.hero h1{font-size:41px}.hero p{font-size:15px}.hero-search{margin-top:22px}.hero-search input{height:54px;font-size:15px;padding-right:48px}.hero-search button{width:42px;height:44px;top:5px;padding:0;font-size:0}.hero-search button:after{content:"→";font-size:18px}.statrow{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.categorygrid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.catcard{min-height:auto}.article-provenance{grid-template-columns:1fr}.article-provenance div{border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}.article-provenance div:last-child{border:0}.filterbar{top:calc(var(--top) + 5px);overflow:auto;flex-wrap:nowrap}.chip{white-space:nowrap}.trustline{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.searchbox{top:5vh;max-height:87vh}}

/* In-page evidence and provenance system */
.evidence-legend{margin:22px 0 28px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);padding:20px 22px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.evidence-legend h2{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman","Songti SC",serif;margin:0 0 8px;font-size:25px}.evidence-legend>p{margin:0 0 16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7}
.evidence-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px}.evidence-item{border-top:4px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface2);padding:14px;min-height:112px}.evidence-item b{display:block;margin:6px 0;font-size:14px}.evidence-item p{font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--muted);margin:0}.evidence-item.official{border-color:#a50d2d}.evidence-item.system{border-color:#315f9f}.evidence-item.community{border-color:#b57d12}.evidence-item.editorial{border-color:#69717c}
.evidence-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;border:1px solid currentColor;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.04em;white-space:nowrap}.evidence-chip.official{color:#a50d2d;background:color-mix(in srgb,#a50d2d 7%,var(--surface))}.evidence-chip.system{color:#315f9f;background:color-mix(in srgb,#315f9f 7%,var(--surface))}.evidence-chip.community{color:#9a680d;background:color-mix(in srgb,#b57d12 8%,var(--surface))}.evidence-chip.editorial{color:var(--muted);background:var(--surface2)}
.article-source-note{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin:14px 0 22px}.article-source-note>span:last-child{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.article-section h2{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px}.section-source{font-family:Arial,"PingFang SC",sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.03em;color:var(--muted);border:1px solid var(--line);padding:3px 7px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap}
.experience-box,.editor-box{margin:20px 0;padding:16px 18px;border-left:4px solid #b57d12;background:color-mix(in srgb,#b57d12 7%,var(--surface))}.editor-box{border-color:#69717c;background:var(--surface2)}.experience-box h2,.editor-box h2{margin-top:0;font-size:18px}.experience-box p,.editor-box p{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px}.experience-box li,.editor-box li{margin:8px 0;line-height:1.65}
.sourcebox{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:18px}.sourcebox details{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface2);padding:0 15px}.sourcebox summary{cursor:pointer;font-weight:800;padding:14px 0}.sourcebox .source-links{padding:0 0 14px}.sourcebox .source-link{background:var(--surface)}
.provenance-policy{margin:18px 0;padding:14px 16px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface2);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted)}
.topicfoot .evidence-chip{font-size:9px}.topicfoot>span:last-child{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px}.source-kind{display:inline-block;margin-top:7px;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent)}
@media(max-width:900px){.evidence-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:560px){.evidence-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.evidence-item{min-height:0}.article-section h2{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}.section-source{margin-top:-4px}}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">
<header class="topbar">
 <div class="brand" data-go="home"><div class="brandmark">US</div><div class="brandtext"><strong>USYD Bible</strong><small>悉尼大学新生终极手册</small></div></div>
 <div class="searchbar"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="m20 20-3.4-3.4"/></svg><input id="globalSearch" placeholder="搜索 423 个主题：学生证、DEC 出勤、选课、租房……" autocomplete="off"><span class="kbd">⌘ K</span><div class="suggestions" id="suggestions"></div></div>
 <div class="topactions"><button class="iconbtn themebtn" id="themeBtn" title="切换主题">◐</button><button class="iconbtn" data-go="checklist" title="清单">✓</button></div>
</header>
<aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar"></aside>
<main class="main">
<section class="view active" id="homeView">
 <div class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">University of Sydney · International student guide</div>
  <h1>找到官方答案，<br>再把事情一步步做完。</h1>
  <p>以悉尼大学、CET、澳大利亚政府和 NSW 政府原始页面为基础，补齐中文学生真正需要的操作路径、等待时间、例外和故障排查。</p>
  <div class="hero-search"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="m20 20-3.4-3.4"/></svg><input id="heroSearch" placeholder="你现在要解决什么？例如：学生证加到 Apple Wallet" autocomplete="off"><button id="heroSearchBtn">搜索</button></div>
  <div class="popular"><span>常用：</span><button data-query="Apple Wallet">Apple Wallet</button><button data-query="My Studies">My Studies</button><button data-query="选课">选课</button><button data-query="出勤">DEC 出勤</button><button data-query="OSHC">OSHC</button></div>
  <div class="actions"><button class="btn primary" data-go="browse">浏览完整知识库</button><button class="btn" data-go="checklist">打开入学清单</button><button class="btn" data-go="sources">了解资料标注</button></div>
  <div class="trustline"><span><b>一手资料优先</b><br>USYD / CET / 政府官网</span><span><b>逐步操作</b><br>路径、按钮、等待时间</span><span><b>最后核验</b><br>2026 年 7 月 21 日</span><span><b>隐私</b><br>清单仅存本机</span></div>
 </div>
 <div class="statrow" id="stats"></div>
 <div class="sectionhead"><div><h2>按场景进入</h2><p>不需要从头读，直接打开当前问题。</p></div></div>
 <div class="categorygrid" id="homeCategories"></div>
 <div class="sectionhead"><div><h2>2026 必须知道的变化与事实</h2><p>最容易被旧攻略误导的部分。</p></div></div>
 <div class="facts" id="facts"></div>
 <div class="disclaimer">本网站不会替代法律、移民、医疗或学校正式意见。时间敏感内容均提供官方来源；遇到个人情况时，请使用官方渠道提交 enquiry，并保存 case number。</div>
</section>
<section class="view" id="browseView"><div class="pagehead"><h1>完整知识库</h1><p id="browseSub"></p></div><div class="filterbar" id="filters"></div><div class="topicgrid" id="topicGrid"></div></section>
<section class="view" id="checklistView"><div class="pagehead"><h1>我的入学清单</h1><p>勾选状态只保存在当前浏览器，不上传任何个人信息。</p></div><div class="progress"><span id="progressBar"></span></div><p id="progressText"></p><button class="btn" onclick="window.print()">打印空白清单</button><div id="checklistGroups"></div><p class="only-print">打印日期：__________________　姓名：__________________</p></section>
<section class="view" id="benefitsView"><div class="pagehead"><h1>免费资源与隐藏福利</h1><p>先把免费权益用满，再决定是否购买付费升级。</p></div><div class="topicgrid" id="benefitGrid"></div></section>
<section class="view" id="sourcesView"><div class="pagehead"><h1>资料来源与可信度</h1><p>正文全部留在本站阅读；这里解释标注规则，并提供可选的原始页面核验入口。</p></div><div id="sourceLegendPage"></div><div class="sourcegrid" id="sourceGrid"></div></section>
<section class="view" id="emergencyView"><div class="pagehead"><h1>紧急与故障处理</h1><p>先保护人身和账户安全，再处理学校流程。</p></div><div class="emergencygrid"><div class="emcard danger"><h3>澳大利亚紧急电话</h3><div class="bigphone">000</div><p>警察、消防、救护。有人身危险、严重伤病或犯罪正在发生时直接拨打。</p></div><div class="emcard"><h3>USYD Student Centre</h3><div class="bigphone" style="color:var(--accent)">1800 793 864</div><p>澳大利亚境内；境外 +61 2 8627 1444。工作日 9:00–17:00。</p></div><div class="emcard"><h3>Campus Security</h3><div class="bigphone" style="font-size:27px;color:var(--accent)">+61 2 9351 3333</div><p>校园安全、夜间护送、可疑行为或校园事故。</p></div><div class="emcard"><h3>生命危机支持</h3><div class="bigphone" style="font-size:31px;color:var(--accent)">13 11 14</div><p>Lifeline Australia，24 小时危机支持。生命危险仍先拨 000。</p></div></div><button class="btn" style="margin-top:20px" onclick="filterEmergency()">查看全部故障处理指南</button></section>
</main>
<nav class="mobilebar"><button data-go="home"><b>⌂</b>首页</button><button data-go="browse"><b>⌕</b>搜索</button><button data-go="checklist"><b>✓</b>清单</button><button data-go="benefits"><b>★</b>福利</button><button data-go="emergency"><b>!</b>紧急</button></nav>
<div class="drawerback" id="drawerBack"></div><aside class="drawer" id="drawer"><button class="iconbtn drawerclose" id="drawerClose">×</button><div id="drawerBody"></div></aside>
