大学主要数字系统的身份凭据，应启用 Okta 并保护密码。","priority":"high","tags":["UniKey","账号"],"source":"systems","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["systems"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-2","category":"systems","title":"设置 Okta MFA","summary":"首次登录时设置多重验证，并添加备用方法，避免换手机后无法登录。","priority":"high","tags":["Okta","MFA"],"source":"mfa","stage":"before","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["mfa"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-3","category":"systems","title":"更换手机前处理 Okta","summary":"在旧设备仍可用时添加新验证方式；不要先清空旧手机再处理 MFA。","priority":"high","tags":["换机","Okta"],"source":"mfa","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["mfa"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-4","category":"systems","title":"学校邮箱怎么登录","summary":"通常通过 Microsoft 365 / Outlook 使用 UniKey 登录；重要通知不要只靠 App 推送。","priority":"high","tags":["邮箱","Outlook"],"source":"email","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["email"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-5","category":"systems","title":"MyUni 是入口而不是唯一记录","summary":"MyUni 集中展示常用链接和信息；正式 enrolment 仍以 Sydney Student 为主。","priority":"medium","tags":["MyUni","入口"],"source":"myuni","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["myuni"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-6","category":"systems","title":"Sydney Student 负责什么","summary":"管理 enrolment、个人信息、units、成绩、费用和多项正式学生记录。","priority":"high","tags":["Sydney Student","记录"],"source":"sydney_student","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["sydney_student"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-7","category":"systems","title":"Canvas 负责什么","summary":"课程公告、材料、作业、测验、rubric、反馈和部分成绩都在 Canvas。","priority":"high","tags":["Canvas","课程"],"source":"canvas","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["canvas"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-8","category":"systems","title":"连接校园 Wi‑Fi","summary":"使用校园网络凭据连接 UniSydney 或 eduroam；不要在仿冒登录页输入 UniKey。","priority":"medium","tags":["WiFi","eduroam"],"source":"wifi","stage":"arrival","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["wifi"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-9","category":"systems","title":"安装 Microsoft 365","summary":"在符合条件期间使用学校许可安装 Office；毕业或离校后授权可能变化。","priority":"medium","tags":["Office","软件"],"source":"software","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["software"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-10","category":"systems","title":"账号被锁怎么办","summary":"停止重复尝试，确认密码和 Okta，再通过官方密码或 ICT 支持流程恢复。","priority":"high","tags":["锁定","密码"],"source":"password","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["password"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-11","category":"systems","title":"公共电脑使用安全","summary":"退出 Office、Canvas 和浏览器账号，不保存密码，敏感文件使用私人设备或加密存储。","priority":"medium","tags":["安全","公共电脑"],"source":"systems","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["systems"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"systems-12","category":"systems","title":"系统维护与缓存问题","summary":"先用无痕窗口、另一浏览器和状态页排查，不要因为旧缓存重复提交表单。","priority":"low","tags":["浏览器","缓存"],"source":"systems","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先确认 UniKey 和密码可用","完成 Okta 双重验证并准备备用方式","逐一登录邮箱、Canvas、MyUni、Sydney Student","失败时记录报错截图并联系 ICT Helpdesk"],"sourceKeys":["systems"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-1","category":"card","title":"数字学生证加入 Apple Wallet","summary":"下载 Transact eAccounts，选择 University of Sydney，用 UniKey 与 Okta 登录后点击 Add to Apple Wallet。","priority":"high","tags":["Apple Wallet","步骤"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card","student_cards","digital_setup"],"officialPath":"Transact eAccounts → University of Sydney → UniKey/Okta → Add to Apple Wallet","prerequisites":["已经完成 enrolment，并已收到 UniKey。","已经设置校园网络凭据和 Okta 多重验证。","学生证照片已经获批；USYD 表示照片通常在 3 个工作日内审核。","iPhone 已登录可用的 Apple ID，并安装最新版 Transact eAccounts。"],"sections":[{"title":"在 iPhone 上添加","items":["在 App Store 下载 Transact eAccounts Mobile。","打开应用，划过启动页后点 Get Started。","搜索并选择 University of Sydney。","使用 University of Sydney 账号登录；验证时可在 Okta 与 eAccounts 之间切换。","回到 eAccounts，点 Add to Apple Wallet。","选择 iPhone，依次完成 Next 和 Agree to Terms & Conditions。","看到已添加成功的通知后点 Done。"]},{"title":"同时添加到 Apple Watch","items":["先完成 iPhone 添加。","回到 eAccounts，再次选择添加凭证。","这次点 Apple Watch，并完成同样的确认流程。","官方允许同一学生证加入 1 台 iPhone 和 1 块 Apple Watch。"]},{"title":"添加后多久可用","items":["建筑门禁和图书馆权限通常在 24 小时内生效。","打印权限通常在激活后 12–24 小时生效。","符合资格的 NSW 交通 concession 证明通常需 2 个工作日生效。"]}],"warnings":["数字卡是可选服务，开通后实体卡仍然有效。","数字学生证不能作为校内正式考试和 in-semester test 的身份证明；考试仍需实体学生证。","保留实体卡作为手机没电、损坏或丢失时的备用。"],"troubleshooting":["找不到 University of Sydney：先更新 eAccounts，再重新搜索。","没有 Add to Apple Wallet：检查 enrolment、照片审批、UniKey 和 Okta 是否均完成。","已添加但门禁或打印不能用：分别等待官方同步时限后再联系 Student Centre。","手机丢失：eAccounts → Settings → Card Management，关闭对应 iPhone 或 Watch 凭证；也可联系 Student Centre。"]},{"id":"card-2","category":"card","title":"一台 iPhone 加一块 Apple Watch","summary":"官方允许把数字卡加入一台 iPhone 和一块 Apple Watch；换设备前先正确停用旧凭证。","priority":"medium","tags":["设备","手表"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-3","category":"card","title":"实体卡仍然有效","summary":"开通数字卡不会自动停用实体卡，两者可以并存。","priority":"medium","tags":["实体卡","数字卡"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-4","category":"card","title":"考试不能只带数字卡","summary":"数字学生证不作为正式考试身份证明；校内考试仍需实体学生证。","priority":"high","tags":["考试","证件"],"source":"card_use","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card_use"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-5","category":"card","title":"学生证可以做什么","summary":"常见用途包括门禁、图书馆、打印复印、SydPay 和部分住宿洗衣服务。","priority":"medium","tags":["门禁","打印"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-6","category":"card","title":"开通后功能可能延迟","summary":"照片、enrolment、门禁或打印系统同步可能需要时间；不要连续重复注册。","priority":"medium","tags":["同步","延迟"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-7","category":"card","title":"照片不通过怎么办","summary":"使用正面、清晰、纯背景、无遮挡照片，并按上传页面要求重新提交。","priority":"medium","tags":["照片","审核"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-8","category":"card","title":"手机丢失如何停卡","summary":"可通过 Transact Card Management、SydPay 或联系 Student Centre 停用指定手机或手表凭证。","priority":"high","tags":["丢失","停用"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-9","category":"card","title":"SydPay 与银行卡不是一回事","summary":"SydPay 是校园储值账户，用于部分打印和消费；充值前确认用途，避免大额余额。","priority":"low","tags":["SydPay","充值"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-10","category":"card","title":"门禁无效的排查顺序","summary":"确认 enrolment 与权限、尝试实体卡、记录建筑和时间，再联系 Campus Assist 或 Student Centre。","priority":"medium","tags":["门禁","故障"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-11","category":"card","title":"换手机的正确顺序","summary":"先在旧设备移除或停用数字凭证，再在新设备重新通过 eAccounts 添加。","priority":"medium","tags":["换机","迁移"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"card-12","category":"card","title":"学生证折扣要看资格","summary":"商家折扣与交通 concession 是不同制度；展示学生证不代表自动获得 NSW 交通优惠。","priority":"medium","tags":["折扣","交通"],"source":"transport","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["先完成 enrolment 和学生证照片审核","用 Transact eAccounts 添加数字卡","分别测试门禁、图书馆和打印功能","考试当天仍携带实体学生证"],"sourceKeys":["transport"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"visa-1","category":"visa","title":"工作时数上限","summary":"Subclass 500 学生在课程进行期间通常最多工作 48 小时/两周；以 VEVO 与 grant letter 为最终依据。","priority":"high","tags":["48小时","工作"],"source":"visa_dha","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"guide","steps":["优