tudies"],"source":"sydney_student","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["sydney_student"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-4","category":"card","title":"没有实体卡能先用数字卡吗？","summary":"符合数字卡条件且照片获批后可以设置；但考试仍需要实体卡。","priority":"high","tags":["FAQ","数字卡"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-5","category":"card","title":"数字卡会让实体卡失效吗？","summary":"不会。数字卡是 opt-in，实体卡仍保持有效。","priority":"medium","tags":["FAQ","实体卡"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-6","category":"card","title":"数字卡能参加考试吗？","summary":"不能作为正式考试和 in-semester test 的身份证明，需要实体学生证。","priority":"high","tags":["FAQ","考试"],"source":"card_use","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["card_use"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-7","category":"card","title":"Apple Wallet 添加后立刻能开门吗？","summary":"可能需要同步；门禁和图书馆通常 24 小时内，打印 12–24 小时。","priority":"medium","tags":["FAQ","同步"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-8","category":"enrol","title":"选课后 Canvas 为什么没有课？","summary":"Canvas 发布可能晚于 enrolment；确认 unit 已保存并等待课程开放。","p