。","priority":"high","tags":["FAQ","租房"],"source":"fairtrading","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["fairtrading"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-33","category":"work","title":"雇主说没有 TFN 就不能付工资？","summary":"不要接受非法安排；联系 ATO/Fair Work 了解正确税务和工资处理。","priority":"high","tags":["FAQ","工资"],"source":"fairwork","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["fairwork"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-34","category":"card","title":"手机没电还能用数字卡吗？","summary":"不能保证所有场景可用；保留实体卡，考试必须使用实体卡。","priority":"medium","tags":["FAQ","电量"],"source":"card","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["card"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-35","category":"cet","title":"语言班能经常请假吗？","summary":"不应这样理解；出勤和学业进度要求严格，缺席需按规定处理。","priority":"high","tags":["FAQ","出勤"],"source":"cet_current","stage":"language","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["cet_current"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-36","category":"assessment","title":"电脑坏了自动算特殊考虑吗？","summary":"不自动。需及时记录、报告并按适用流程申请。","priority":"high","tags":["FAQ","电脑"],"source":"special","stage":"all","verified":"2026-07-21","type":"faq","steps":["先查个人文件与登录后系统","再查官方公开页面","仍不明确时提交官方 enquiry","保存 case number 与书面回复"],"sourceKeys":["special"],"officialPath":"","prerequisites":[],"sections":[],"warnings":[],"troubleshooting":[]},{"id":"faq-37","category":"systems","title":"Canvas 和 Sydney Student 成绩一样吗？","summar